{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":906310,"duration_api_ms":687611,"num_turns":78,"result":"## Summary\n\n**Bug:** `OrderConfirmationScreen` didn't appear after order submission in hall mode. Instead, the Drawer (cart overlay) stayed visible showing \"Ваши заказы (1)\".\n\n**Root Cause:** The `OrderConfirmationScreen` was rendered as a regular inline `<div>` inside the page content flow. The shadcn/vaul `Drawer` component renders as a **portal overlay** with `z-index: 50`. Even though `showConfirmation()` correctly set `drawerMode=null` (triggering the Drawer's close animation) and `view=\"confirmation\"`, the Drawer's exit animation and portal stacking kept it visually on top of the confirmation screen the entire time.\n\n**Fix:** Wrapped `OrderConfirmationScreen` in a fixed full-screen overlay container:\n```jsx\n<div className=\"fixed inset-0 z-[60] bg-white overflow-y-auto\">\n  <div className=\"px-4 py-8 max-w-md mx-auto ...\">\n    ... confirmation content ...\n  </div>\n</div>\n```\n\n- `fixed inset-0` — covers entire viewport\n- `z-[60]` — above Drawer's z-50 overlay\n- `bg-white` — opaque background, nothing shows through\n- `overflow-y-auto` — scrollable if content exceeds viewport\n\n**Output:** `pages/PublicMenu/260303-02 x RELEASE.jsx`  \n**Git:** `63859d5` pushed to main  \n**Codex:** timed out (120s)","stop_reason":null,"session_id":"269daeba-b57b-4a61-8c7e-c324b3849ad7","total_cost_usd":3.8491454999999997,"usage":{"input_tokens":68,"cache_creation_input_tokens":100174,"cache_read_input_tokens":4781252,"output_tokens":32620,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":100174,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"modelUsage":{"claude-opus-4-6":{"inputTokens":68,"outputTokens":32620,"cacheReadInputTokens":4781252,"cacheCreationInputTokens":100174,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":3.